{"tid":648874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟3】結局太驚嚇觀眾要心理輔導  有人激動暈倒送院","createTime":"2018-05-01T06:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T12:28:24.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6cde64658c61635abbee161bc2287309ef67b75","tid":648874,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"Marvel十年大作《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War，下稱《復仇者3》）已上映數日，未知各位觀眾入場睇戲未？對電影結局又有何感想？美國有不少觀眾看完《復仇者3》十分激動，不單有人話要接受心理輔導，更有觀眾散場時暈倒送院。<br />\n<br />\n美國比香港遲兩日才上映《復仇者3》，觀眾看過電影後紛紛於社交網站分享感想，雖然絕大部分都好守規矩沒劇透，但幾乎所有人都對結局表示震驚，以下節錄的反應相當有趣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404138/org/467b78be6b24489f23ec2c5c7da0de5b.jpg/BYWdH4S9AiWXqEInG-ziqpMZgYhojIB8JY8jqSWPI6k?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404138%2Forg%2F467b78be6b24489f23ec2c5c7da0de5b.jpg%2FBYWdH4S9AiWXqEInG-ziqpMZgYhojIB8JY8jqSWPI6k%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=52b57e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404140/org/68f0bb0e388e00c23e1befbee295f1ff.jpg/l-PyAo7lYo_AcQmbNJvM_uLShBeEPOYovr--cb6_vnE?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404140%2Forg%2F68f0bb0e388e00c23e1befbee295f1ff.jpg%2Fl-PyAo7lYo_AcQmbNJvM_uLShBeEPOYovr--cb6_vnE%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=766ffeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404144/org/be7784fc24734c79f2cdea72e99a25ae.jpg/C3XKsAsBOLfOWkAfX87-rCFohszmqLSVHShoix0oaIs?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404144%2Forg%2Fbe7784fc24734c79f2cdea72e99a25ae.jpg%2FC3XKsAsBOLfOWkAfX87-rCFohszmqLSVHShoix0oaIs%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=95d69cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404145/org/73a55133f4baabb38037d768a2637590.jpg/X7Gu79Gb1a2sSOPSN1NPUYore-srL0kZqCzP2agsz9k?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404145%2Forg%2F73a55133f4baabb38037d768a2637590.jpg%2FX7Gu79Gb1a2sSOPSN1NPUYore-srL0kZqCzP2agsz9k%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=624417ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404151/org/9a93670cd64a1e76423bd70b56245161.jpg/ZJ35Lu5oCQYhgqIFcpEIIB7SamwymUmbL6oALi-qAC4?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404151%2Forg%2F9a93670cd64a1e76423bd70b56245161.jpg%2FZJ35Lu5oCQYhgqIFcpEIIB7SamwymUmbL6oALi-qAC4%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=7786d712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404153/org/08919c970e86b48e47d21cdcc23da69a.jpg/m8ceRrdaAuMm9ShRL0lw0uNTSJoz1qTskwB_UJMAf1A?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404153%2Forg%2F08919c970e86b48e47d21cdcc23da69a.jpg%2Fm8ceRrdaAuMm9ShRL0lw0uNTSJoz1qTskwB_UJMAf1A%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=ed1ac476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404098/org/29041ae065c71cdb08c1886ff2603eab.jpg/YbnvPUvDJhCReqns5IxWYfgkc0bhoh3ywQRKvMEESrw?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404098%2Forg%2F29041ae065c71cdb08c1886ff2603eab.jpg%2FYbnvPUvDJhCReqns5IxWYfgkc0bhoh3ywQRKvMEESrw%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=1a0700b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民甚至分享某位觀眾看完《復仇者3》後昏倒被送院的場面，究竟結局有幾驚嚇先會令觀眾有咁大反應？已入場的你應該心中有數，而為了未入場的你著想，在此不作劇透，但作個最壞打算當心理準備亦無防。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9a7a905bc43cc7bac685888b62c3290ce7f50c","tid":648874,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"打手味/廣告味濃"},{"pid":"ec42bd9314f011d18b5905781fcec1713ae62694","tid":648874,"uid":117837,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-0